text: Alexia Arisarah Schenkel (born 15 December 1996) is a Thai alpine skier. She competed in slalom and giant slalom at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Thai female alpine skiers Category:Thai people of Swiss descent Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Thailand Category:Alpine skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
